name: Full Set; Desk Tidies by Clea Jentsch
description:
Collection shortlisted for InteriorsUK New Design Britain Awards

The full Desk Tidies Set is available to purchase as well as the individual components.

Only 10 limited edition sets were produced by Clea, all designed and lovingly crafted by this talented new designer.

If you are interested in purchasing the full set, please drop us a line: us@looklikelove.co.uk

Clea Jentsch (www.cleajentsch.co.uk) has developed a collection of pared down desk tidies.  Each object has been folded from a single piece of mild steel. 

The collection is characterised by its simplicity, having been reduced down to solely include the necessary. While the objects are very unostentatious, each piece has a twist in how it functions or can be used. 
Subtle details suggest secondary functions and invite the user to defy convention.

The collection, comprising of seven different objects, has been developed through model-making straight into the end material, mild steel. The restrictions of the sheet metal folder have led many of the design decisions. A similar visual language running through the entire collection ties it together. 

This first edition has been laser cut from mild steel, folded and then powder coated in matt pastel green and zinc yellow.

name: Aduke Rectangle Cushion from House of Arike
description:
Unique African printed cotton cushion cover with piping comes with a duck-feather filled cushion pad. 

Each cushion is handmade so pattern placement may differ slightly from the image. 

Slight runs and inconsistencies are a natural outcome of the African printing process, merely adding to the charm of these pieces.

Size: Rectangle Cushion (with piping) - 30cmx60cm / 12"x24"

Care Instructions: Filling - Duck Feather (Dry clean only)
Wash cover inside out at 30° with similar colours and use a medium iron temperature.

Note: Cushions are available in any of the featured materials, plain or piped to any size, and made to order. 

Contact us via email with your bespoke order

name: Baby Booties in Forest Green with Silver Stars by Accidental Vix
description:
A warm welcome to Vicky, also know as Accidental Vix. 

We are excited to introduce a new baby section to the shop, and a pleasure to have a small collection of these hand-made booties...

They have been designed as pram shoes, for keeping feet warm and not for walking in. There is a fleece insole for extra warmth, denim sole and cotton outer.

They are designed to stay on snug as they have elastic at the ankles. These are approx 100mm - 4” in length on the sole, which is Vicky's standard 3-6 months, but please note this is only a guideline, as all babies feet vary so would advise measuring your little one's feet before ordering.

Colour: Silver stars on green
Size: To fit 3-6 months (approx)
Material: 100% Cotton with felt internal and a soft denim sole
Washing Instructions: Washable up to 40º

They have been designed as pram shoes, for keeping feet warm and not for walking in. There is a fleece insole for extra warmth, denim sole and cotton outer.

They are designed to stay on snug as they have elastic at the ankles. These are approx 100mm - 4” in length on the sole, which is Vicky's standard 3-6 months, but please note this is only a guideline, as all babies feet vary so would advise measuring your little one's feet before ordering.

Size: To fit 3-6 months (approx)
Material: 100% Cotton with felt internal and a soft denim sole
Washing Instructions: Washable up to 40º

description:
